{"tid":1633848,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"簡單分辨人話鬼話","createTime":"2019-10-07T05:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T10:21:23.000Z","uid":176637,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"046c35439a11e01fb9b8bddadca578a85e13bc85","tid":1633848,"uid":176637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:29:43.000Z","msg":"有幾樣心得分辨人同鬼<br />\n1.和勇係團結一心，分化說話係唔會講。其實和勇已經係命運共同體，係唔可能尋日撐你，今日就割蓆，譴責。<br />\n2.大家信奉言論自由，所以說話會尊重相方，挑釁性/怪責性說話9成係鬼話。<br />\n3.善用，理性，邏輯，獨立思考，批判性思考，唔好比憤怒/仇恨掩蓋雙眼。<br />\n4.勇武唔想和理非受傷/被捕，而和理非亦唔會想勇武受傷/被捕，所以武力升級，煽動既說話係好鬼。<br />\n5. be humble."},{"pid":"c22862f99f482c9de75694f5f2a9ea504e4e7d46","tid":1633848,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:30:09.000Z","msg":"有時唔洗下下硬打既，轉個方式抗爭都得<br />\n比勇武叉叉電 比文宣組做下野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631757</a>"},{"pid":"ef3a655fbfed0dd7a4b1fdd9efe96d912eec5e56","tid":1633848,"uid":22796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:32:24.000Z","msg":"一直都叫大家唔好互屌<br />\n<br />\n不割席 不分化<br />\n唔係得個講字 真係要銘記於心"},{"pid":"cf610d89c62056e55ff11d587f26bb9b7c3bbcb2","tid":1633848,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:36:32.000Z","msg":"岩"},{"pid":"f7132e68d1e18f5644cf23eeee7793bbc3726423","tid":1633848,"uid":176637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:40:36.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"14424442ebea8a35d7720cac5e4ee30b44d912fd","tid":1633848,"uid":301327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T06:57:15.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2e61b8bc94d6e874e7d4c122b89e11d10349cc75","tid":1633848,"uid":176637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T10:21:23.000Z","msg":"自推"}]}